docs {
  ## Patch Price List (Config)
  อัปเดตข้อมูลรายการราคาที่มีอยู่

  Modifies an existing vendor price list, such as updating product prices, validity dates, or adding new product lines. Updated prices are used in subsequent purchase order creation.

  ### Path Parameters
  | Name | Type | Description |
  |------|------|-------------|
  | `bu_code` | string | Business unit code |
  | `id` | string (UUID) | Price list ID |

  ### Headers
  | Name | Required | Description |
  |------|----------|-------------|
  | `Authorization` | Yes | `Bearer {{access_token}}` |
  | `x-app-id` | Yes | `{{x_app_id}}` |

  ### Permissions
  - **Permission key**: `vendor_management.price_list:update`
  - **Roles**: Purchase

  ### Sample Body
  ```json
  {
    "id": "019638a6-2a00-7c4f-8e46-9b7a52c80c4d",
    "pricelist_no": "PL-2026-0001",
    "name": "Q2 2026 Vendor Price List (Revised)",
    "description": "Quarterly price agreement for dry goods — revised",
    "status": "active",
    "vendor_id": "019638a6-2a00-7c4f-8e46-9b7a52c80c4d",
    "currency_id": "019638a6-2a00-7c4f-8e46-9b7a52c80c4d",
    "currency_code": "THB",
    "effective_from_date": "2026-04-01T00:00:00.000Z",
    "effective_to_date": "2026-06-30T00:00:00.000Z",
    "is_active": true,
    "doc_version": 1,
    "pricelist_detail": {
      "add": [],
      "update": [{"id": "019638a6-2a00-7c4f-8e46-9b7a52c80c4d", "price_without_tax": 260.00, "price": 278.20}],
      "delete": []
    }
  }
  ```

  ### Sample Response
  ```json
  {
    "data": {
      "id": "019638a6-2a00-7c4f-8e46-9b7a52c80c4d"
    },
    "paginate": null,
    "status": 200,
    "success": true,
    "message": "Success",
    "timestamp": "2026-04-29T08:30:00.000Z"
  }
  ```

  ### Error Responses
  | Status | When |
  |--------|------|
  | 400 | Request body fails validation |
  | 401 | Bearer token is missing or invalid |
  | 403 | User lacks `vendor_management.price_list:update` permission |
  | 404 | Price list with the specified ID not found |

  > Service-layer errors propagate via TCP; see micro-business for full list.
}

